# 检查数据信息
def check_data(data,data_name):
    
    print('{:*^50}'.format('{}数据信息').format(data_name))
    print(data.info()) 
    
    print('\n','字段唯一值数量:')    
    for column in data.columns:
        print('{}:'.format(column),len(data[column].unique()))
    
    print('\n','字段是否含空值')
    print(data.isnull().any(axis=0))
    
    print('\n','\n')

特征工程¶

In [10]:
def features_proceed(data):
    
    #将字符统一转换为数字
    maps = {'0':0, 'a':1, 'b':2, 'c':3, 'd':4}
    data.StoreType.replace(maps, inplace=True)
    data.Assortment.replace(maps, inplace=True)
    data.StateHoliday.replace(maps, inplace=True)
    
    #对时间进行拆分，并添加新的特征
    data['Year'] = data.Date.dt.year
    data['Month'] = data.Date.dt.month
    data['Day'] = data.Date.dt.day
    data['DayOfWeek'] = data.Date.dt.dayofweek
    data['WeekOfYear'] = data.Date.dt.weekofyear
    
    return data
 

#对训练，保留以及测试数据集进行特征转化
features_proceed(train)
features_proceed(test)

In [15]:
#resample:对Date日期截取到月，然后根据这个截取字段 进行统计。（M:表示截取到月， kind='period'：表示Date是日期字段）
da3=train.groupby('Date')['Sales'].mean().resample('M', kind='period').mean().reset_index()
fig=plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))
ax=fig.add_subplot(1,1,1)

sns.pointplot(data=da3, x='Date', y='Sales', ax=ax)
plt.xticks(rotation=45)
ax.set_title('商店每月平均销售额情况')
Out[15]:

定义评价函数¶

In [28]:
 #定义评价函数rmspe
def rmspe(y, yhat):
    return np.sqrt(np.mean((np.divide(np.subtract(y, yhat),y))**2))
    
def rmspe_xg(yhat, y):
    y = np.expm1(y.get_label())
    yhat = np.expm1(yhat)
    return "rmspe", rmspe(y,yhat)

模型构建¶

In [144]:
start = time()

#训练次数
train_rounds = 1
for num in range(train_rounds):
    
    #参数设定
    params = {"objective": "reg:linear",
              "booster" : "gbtree",
              "eta": 0.02,                     #学习率
              "max_depth": 10,                 #树最大深度
              "subsample": 0.9,                #随机选取样本的比率
              "colsample_bytree": 0.7,         #随机选取特征的比率（构造树时） 
              "silent": 1,                     #只打印警告信息
              "seed": 78
              }
    #每次训练数量
    num_boost_round = 5000

    # 转换为训练数据与验证数据
    dtrain = xgb.DMatrix(x_train, y_train)
    dvalid = xgb.DMatrix(x_valid, y_valid)

    #观察列表
    watchlist = [(dtrain, 'train'), (dvalid, 'valid')]

    #模型训练
    start = time()

    gbm = xgb.train(params, dtrain, num_boost_round, evals=watchlist, 
      early_stopping_rounds=100, feval=rmspe_xg, verbose_eval=True)

end = time()
print('训练时间： {:2f} 小时.'.format((end-start)/3600))

#存储验证集预测结果 
save_valid_pred_info = pd.DataFrame(data = y_valid)
save_valid_pred_info['Prediction']=yhat_valid
# 通过index索引 将数据连接起来
save_valid_pred_info = pd.merge(x_valid, save_valid_pred_info, left_index= True, right_index=True)
save_valid_pred_info['Ratio'] = save_valid_pred_info.Prediction/save_valid_pred_info.Sales
save_valid_pred_info['Error'] =(save_valid_pred_info.Ratio-1)
save_valid_pred_info['Error-abs'] =abs(save_valid_pred_info.Ratio-1)
save_valid_pred_info['Weight'] = save_valid_pred_info.Sales/save_valid_pred_info.Prediction

print('所有商店均值比率(Sale/Prediction)：{}'.format(save_valid_pred_info.Ratio.mean()))
save_valid_pred_info.head()[['Sales','Prediction','Ratio','Error','Weight']]

模型优化¶

#查看基本权重范围
base_weight = 1 - abs(save_valid_pred_info.Ratio.mean() -1)

#设置基本权重
base_weight = int(base_weight *100)/100
base_weight
Out[152]:
0.99
In [153]:
W=[(base_weight+(i/1000)) for i in range(50)]

偏差整体校正优化¶

In [154]:
S =[]
for w in W:
    error = rmspe(np.expm1(y_valid), np.expm1(yhat_valid*w))
    S.append(error)
   
Score = pd.Series(S, index = W)
Score.plot()

#整体校正rmpse 分数
valid_rmpse_1 = Score[Score.values == Score.values.min()].values[0]
best_weight =  Score[Score.values == Score.values.min()].index[0]

print('校正前rmpse:  {}'.format(valid_rmspe))
print('校正后rmpse:  {}'.format(valid_rmpse_1))

校正前rmpse:  0.1263255149770075
校正后rmpse:  0.12092573646269592
In [155]:
save_valid_pred_info['weight_entirety'] =  best_weight.repeat(len(save_valid_pred_info)).tolist()
save_valid_pred_info['Pred_entirety'] = save_valid_pred_info['Prediction'] * best_weight

分组偏差优化¶

In [158]:
store_id = []
store_pred_w = []

store_id.clear()
store_id.clear()

for s in range(1115): 
    #指定商店ID 的 验证数据
    s1 = pd.DataFrame(save_valid_pred_info[save_valid_pred_info['Store']==s+1],columns = ['Sales','Prediction']) 

    S =[]       
    for w in W:
        error = rmspe(np.expm1(s1.Sales), np.expm1(s1.Prediction*w))
        S.append(error)
        
    #获得商店的 最佳权重
    Score = pd.Series(S,index=W)
    BS = Score[Score.values == Score.values.min()]              

    #存储权重信息
    store_id.append(s+1)
    store_pred_w.extend(BS.index.values)
In [159]:
#每个商店的最佳
store_weight = pd.DataFrame(data = store_id, columns=['Store'])
store_weight['weight_store']=  pd.Series(store_pred_w)
In [160]:
# 合并数据
save_valid_pred_info = pd.merge(save_valid_pred_info, store_weight, on='Store')

# 分组偏差预测

test_pred = pd.merge(test_pred, store_weight, on='Store')

result = pd.DataFrame({"Id": test['Id'], 'Sales': np.expm1(test_pred.Prediction * test_pred.weight_store)})
result.to_csv("kaggle-submit/Rossmann_submit3.csv", index=False)
